quran[28]{c,v,t}:
  74,48,"Dinzuɣu, suhudeenim’ suhudee ku tooi niŋ ba anfaani shεli (Zaadali)"
  74,49,"Bo n-leei mali ba (chεfurnim’ maa), ka bɛ lebri biriti wa’azu (Alkur’aani)"
  74,50,"Bɛ (chεfurinim’ maa yi nya Annabi Muhammadu), bɛ ŋmanila buŋ’ shɛŋa ban yirigi"
  74,51,Ka bɛ zo ka chɛ gbiɣinli
  74,52,Chɛli gba! Bɛ (chεfurinim’ maa) zaɣiyino kam bɔrimi ni bɛ ti ba gbana (litaafi na Naawuni sani) ka di yɛrgi luɣulikam
  74,53,Haifa! Chɛli gba! Bɛ kuli bi zɔrila Chiyaama
  74,54,Haifa! Achiika! Di (Alkur’aani) nyɛla teebu
  74,55,"Dinzuɣu, ninvuɣu so ŋun bɔra, tɔ! Ŋun zaŋmi li n-teei o maŋa"
  74,56,"Yaha! Bɛ (chɛfurinim’) bi zaŋdi li n-teeri bɛ maŋa, naɣila Naawuni yi yu, Ŋuna n-nyɛ Ŋun tu ni bɛ zo dabiεm, ka lahi nyɛ Ŋun tu kamaata ni chεmpaŋ"
  75,1,M (Mani Naawuni) po Zaadali
  75,2,Yaha! M-po nyɛvuli shɛli din zooi di maŋ’ galime
  75,3,"Di ni bɔŋɔ, ninsala (chɛfura) tεhirimi ni Ti (Tinim’ Naawuni) ku tooi laɣim o koba (Zaadali)"
  75,4,Wumma! Ti (Tinim’ Naawuni) nyɛla ban yɛn tooi laɣim o nubihi mini o naponbihi luɣuyini
  75,5,Chɛli gba! Ninsala (chɛfura) bɔrimi ni o daŋsi tuumbεri o tooni
  75,6,"Ka o naan bɔhira: “Bondali n-nyɛ Zaadali?”"
  75,7,Di yi ti niŋ ka nimbihi nyεɣisi
  75,8,Ka goli neesim chaŋ ka chɛ li
  75,9,Ka bɛ laɣim wuntaŋ’ mini goli (ka di yi wulinpuhili na)
  75,10,"Dindali maa ka ninsala yɛn ti yεli: “Yapolo ka guubu shee be?”"
  75,11,Haifa! Sɔɣibu shee ti kani
  75,12,"Dindali maa, a Duuma (Naawuni) sani n-nyɛ tablibu shee"
  75,13,"Dindali maa, ka bɛ yɛn ti ninsala o ni daŋsi tuun’ shɛli (o nyɛvuli puuni), ni o ni naɣisi shɛli lahibali"
  75,14,Chɛli gba! Ninsala gba nya o tuma ni nyɛ shɛli
  75,15,Hali o yi ti tahi o fabla na (bɛ ku deei li)
  75,16,"(Yaa nyini Annabi)! Di damdi a zinli (ni Alkur’aani karimbu), domin a gbaai li ni yomyoma"
  75,17,"Achiika! Ti (Tinim’ Naawuni) n-su di laɣimbu (a zuɣu ni), ni di karimbu"
  75,18,"Dinzuɣu, Ti yi karindi li, tɔ! Nyin doli di karimbu maa (ni baalim)"
  75,19,"Din nyaaŋa, Tinima n-su di neebu"